# =========================================================================
# 🌟 BOMB CRYPTO MARKETPLACE - OPEN SOURCE ENVIRONMENT
# =========================================================================
# Welcome, Contributor!
#
# To get started locally without setting up a full database:
# 1. Copy this file to `.env.development`
# 2. Run `pnpm dev`
#
# By default, the Pulse Dashboards will use this VITE_API_BASE_URL to fetch
# live read-only data from the production network, allowing you to build and
# test the UI instantly!
# =========================================================================

# Note: Since the real live API strictly checks CORS, we use the local proxy
# set up in vite.config.ts for the VITE_API_BASE_URL during development
# so requests go through `http://localhost:3004/pulse-api/bsc` safely!
VITE_API_BASE_URL=/pulse-api/bsc
